{"tid":1072180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[贏］外媒指特朗普要求中國增購美國貨一至兩倍","createTime":"2019-03-22T00:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T01:37:09.000Z","uid":50386,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"76a6641128671aba5b7829ad3cda0e05122ef9de","tid":1072180,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T00:45:16.000Z","msg":"據《CNBC》引述消息人士報道，美國總統特朗普致力透過中美貿易談判降低貿易赤字，正指示白宮談判代表要求中國未來增加進口美國商品一倍至兩倍。<br />\n<br />\n中國早前已提出在未來六年，向美方採購合共總值1.2萬億美元商品，包括能源、農業和航空產品。不過隨本月初美國公布的貿易數據，去年對華貿易赤字達到4,190億美元破紀錄，按年增長12%，令到特朗普期望中方的進口金額加碼，消息人士指特朗普要求的購買美國貨規模，是較中方建議的1.2萬億美元，高出一倍至兩倍，以助特朗普爭取明年連任總統。<br />\n<br />\n爆買美國貨<br />\n支那又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95876310fd28a8b447c4f4bf66164c0702a17ce","tid":1072180,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T00:52:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d97bc2b7a19df9a34e0bd7fc35c0b5267688e30","tid":1072180,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"美國有無咁多實貨出口呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5daf6aa760e6e3aedb908c656b70c64778af4140","tid":1072180,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d97bc2b7a19df9a34e0bd7fc35c0b5267688e30","tid":1072180,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"美國有無咁多實貨出口呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:07:23.000Z","msg":"支那爆買搞到美國造唔切要違約<br />\n支那又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec71823cf2809f808111b61260f37ec95c94b05","tid":1072180,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:24:44.000Z","msg":"現代版割地賠款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cdf04e7fdb7ee2b5f44856aaf55de96ce9033b","tid":1072180,"uid":21035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo